WEBVTT

00:05:58.160 --> 00:06:02.176
psixopatiyadan o'zgacha miya ta’sirida 
yuz berishi mumkinmi?

00:06:02.200 --> 00:06:04.440
Psixopatiyaga qaysidir jihatdan teskari

00:06:05.880 --> 00:06:08.976
miya, yuz ifodasiga ta’sirchan amigdala va

00:06:09.000 --> 00:06:11.416
ehtimol o’rtacha miyadan 
yirikroq miya o'zgalar

00:06:11.440 --> 00:06:13.280
qo’rquvini yaxshiroq
ilg'ashi mumkinmi?

00:06:13.920 --> 00:06:15.936
Tadqiqotlarim natijasi bularning barchasi

00:06:15.960 --> 00:06:17.416
haqiqat ekanligini ko’rsatdi.

00:06:17.440 --> 00:06:18.696
Biz bu natijaga chinakam

00:06:18.720 --> 00:06:21.736
altruist insonlarni sinovdan o'tkazib

00:06:21.760 --> 00:06:24.416
erishdik. Ular o’z buyraklaridan 
birini butkul

00:06:24.440 --> 00:06:25.640
notanishga berishgan.

00:06:26.600 --> 00:06:29.696
Buyraklaridan birining jarrohlik bilan

00:06:29.720 --> 00:06:32.336
olinib, ehtimol qachon ko'rishmaydigan